name: Videonewmedia
tag_list: business-magazine, press-release-center, business-updates, product-news, newswire, news-services, business-publication
overview:
Videonewmedia.com fulfills the objectives and demands of many small and medium sized companies looking for free and affordable business-only online publication that will help spread stories about their businesses, products, services and other information critical to their business success. This site however is not only limited to the SMEs but also open to all large and public listed companies which finds this site helpful and important part of their media campaign.

Stories can be in the form of articles, press releases, advertorials, video advertisements, investor relation news, product announcements, anything that will help your potential customers see the true capabilities and offerings provided by your company. The site also provides for publication of video based news and advertisements.
